Chapter 1 : Doll house

" Once upon a dream

There is a cute little girl. 

Who wounded inside by swear words and violence from her family whenever she made a mistake even a little.

Her upper face mouth have a hair flow out. Mean that she want to scream and let out emotion to tell everyone that she in pain. But that will cause her family to angry at her

So she have to be silence and act perfectly like a doll.

Waiting to be played or torn apart "
